title: H.Exe - Human Flesh Recipes 2014 dark electro industrial goth
description:
H.Exe's latest album is a must-have item on the playlist of every serious follower of dark electro scene. Immaculate production and insane levels of aggression are just the beginning, so listen at your own risk.

Human Flesh Recipes is second full-length release of the band. There is no searching or copying somebody else's style, they know exactly how they want to sound and what results they want to achieve.

More info: www.halotan.net
